{"url":"https://www.iwatani.co.jp/jpn/recruit/career/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n\r\n\r\n<html lang=\"ja\">\r\n<head>\r\n\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=yes\">\r\n<title>\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\tキャリア採用 | 岩谷産業 - Iwatani Corporation\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\r\n</title>\r\n\r\n<!-- description -->\r\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"岩谷産業株式会社の採用情報です。岩谷産業株式会社の採用に関する情報から、社員紹介、事業内容などをご覧いただけます。\">\r\n\r\n<!-- keywords -->\r\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"岩谷産業、岩谷、イワタニ、Iwatani、iwatani corporation、採用、新卒採用、インターン、インターンシップ、商社、専門商社、水素、エネルギー\" />\r\n\r\n<!-- copyright -->\r\n<meta name=\"copyright\" content=\"&copy; Iwatani Corporation. All Rights Reserved.\">\r\n\r\n<!-- OGP -->\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"岩谷産業 - Iwatani Corporation\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.iwatani.co.jp/jpn/recruit/\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"岩谷産業 - Iwatani Corporation\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.iwatani.co.jp/jpn/recruit/\" />\r\n\r\n<!-- favicon -->\r\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"../assets/images/common/favicon.ico\" />\r\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"../assets/images/common/favicon.png\">\r\n<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"../assets/images/common/favicon.png\">\r\n<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"../assets/images/common/favicon.png\">\r\n\r\n<!-- source -->\r\n<link href=\"../assets/css/style.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n<link href=\"../assets/css/other.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js\"></script>\r\n\r\n<link href=\"../assets/css/slick.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\